line_1: Collects his spades, his mattocks and his hoes,
line_2: The short'ning winter-day is near a close;

line_1: Collects his spades, his mattocks and his hoes,
line_2: The black'ning trains o' craws to their repose:

line_1: Collects his spades, his mattocks and his hoes,
line_2: The toil-worn COTTER frae his labor goes,

line_1: And after setting sun his garden hoes;
line_2: Who trains the vine that round his window grows,
